ta"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"When you or your connected accounts communicate with other people, we store the counterparties' name, phone number, email address, message history, tags, notes, pipeline/deal stage, and any custom fields you add, so you can manage those relationships inside the Service."}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-base font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2","children":"2.5 Messages, broadcasts, and attachments"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We store the content of emails and WhatsApp messages sent and received through the Service, along with file attachments (stored in our object storage), and aggregate delivery/read statistics for broadcast campaigns you create."}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-base font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2","children":"2.6 Usage data"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We automatically collect log data such as IP address, browser type, device information, pages visited, and timestamps, to operate, secure, and improve the Service."}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-base font-semibold text-indigo-700 mt-6 mb-2","children":"2.7 Cookies"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We use essential cookies/local storage to keep you signed in and remember preferences. We do not use third-party advertising cookies."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-3","children":"3. How we use information"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We use the information above to:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":"Provide, operate, and maintain the unified inbox, contacts, broadcasts, automations, and analytics features"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Authenticate you and keep your account secure"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Sync and deliver email and WhatsApp messages on your behalf"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Respond to support requests"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Monitor and improve the reliability and performance of the Service"}],["$","li",null,{"children":"Comply with legal obligations"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We do not sell your personal information or Google user data, and we do not use it to serve ads."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-3","children":"4. How we share information"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We share information only with:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Google, Microsoft, and Meta"}]," — to the extent necessary to send/receive email or WhatsApp messages through their APIs on your instruction"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Infrastructure and sub-processors"}]," we use to run the Service (database, object storage, and hosting providers), under confidentiality obligations, solely to provide the Service"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"Law enforcement or regulators"}],", if required by law, subpoena, or to protect the rights, property, or safety of Medha Labs, our users, or the public"]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"A successor entity"}],", if Medha Labs is involved in a merger, acquisition, or sale of assets, subject to this policy or a materially equivalent one"]}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"We never sell personal data or Google user data to third parties, and we never share it for third-party advertising or unrelated purposes."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-3","children":"5. Data storage and security"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":"Data is stored in our PostgreSQL database and object storage, protected by access controls and encryption. OAuth tokens (including Google refresh/access tokens) and email account passwords are encrypted at rest. No method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security."}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-3","children":"6. Data retention and deletion"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["We retain your account data, connected-account tokens, and message/contact data for as long as your account remains active, so the Service can continue to function. If you delete your account or request deletion by emailing"," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"mailto:medhalabs04@gmail.com","className":"text-indigo-600 hover:underline","children":"medhalabs04@gmail.com"}],", we will delete or anonymize your personal data, connected-account tokens, and associated messages within 30 days, except where we are required to retain limited records for legal or security purposes."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Disconnecting a Google account in-app, or revoking Medha Sync's access from your"," ",["$","a",null,{"href":"https://myaccount.google.com/permissions","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","className":"text-indigo-600 hover:underline","children":"Google Account permissions page"}],", immediately stops further access and triggers deletion of the stored tokens for that account."]}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-10 mb-3","children":"7. Your rights"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4","children":["Depending on your location, you m